colorPalette:
This category identifies **dominant and accent colors visible** in the creative. Report 3–6 main colors. Focus on the hues you actually see, not emotions or brand meanings. Output valid JSON array:
[
  {"color_name": "navy blue", "hex_code": "#000080", "role": "dominant"},
  {"color_name": "beige", "hex_code": "#F5F5DC", "role": "accent"}
]
Rules: no commentary; include only color name, hex code, and role (dominant/accent).
